<p class="orange">Searching through historic newspapers from 23 European countries</p>

<p>December 3, 2014 &#151; &quot;As part of the Europeana Newspapers project, The <a href="http://www.theeuropeanlibrary.org/tel4/">European Library</a> developed a <a href="http://www.theeuropeanlibrary.org/tel4/newspapers">historic newspapers browser</a> that enables users to perform full-text searches in millions of historic newspaper pages....&quot;</p>

